{"title":"Skin Electrica lImpedance Model for Evaluation of the Thickness and Water Content of the Stratum Corneum","uid":"8777cc66a6ad4610cfd0b122b7c5b7a0","slug":"文献阅读/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum","date":"2023-10-22T04:33:17.000Z","updated":"2023-10-22T04:24:48.676Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/文献阅读/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/covers/ReadPaper.png","content":"<h3 id=\"论文基本信息\"><a href=\"#论文基本信息\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"论文基本信息\"></a>论文基本信息</h3><p>第一作者：Osamu UEHARA, Toshimasa KUSUHARA,Kenichi MATSUZAKI, Yoshitake YAMAMOTO, Takao NAKAMURA</p>\n<p>引用格式：[1]Osamu U,Toshimasa K,Kenichi M, et al. Skin Electrical Impedance Model for Evaluation of the Thickness and Water Content of the Stratum Corneum[J]. Advanced Biomedical Engineering,2022,11(0).</p>\n<p>作者背景：Medical Engineering Laboratory, ALCARE CO., Ltd.;Department of Radiological Technology, Graduate School of Health Sciences, Okayama University</p>\n<p>链接：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/abe/11/0/11_11_98/_article\">Skin Electrical Impedance Model for Evaluation of the Thickness and Water Content of the Stratum Corneum</a></p>\n<p>关键词：皮肤电阻抗、厚度、含水量、角质层、皮肤屏障。</p>\n<p><a href=\"%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/Skin+Electrical+Impedance+Model+for+Evaluation+of+the+Thickness+and+Water+Content+of+the+Stratum+Corneum.pdf\">Skin Electrical Impedance Model for Evaluation of the Thickness and Water Content of the Stratum Corneum.pdf</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"摘要\"><a href=\"#摘要\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"摘要\"></a>摘要</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>皮肤屏障功能的恶化导致了过敏症状，因为各种化学物质可能进入人体。在领域如皮肤科、护理学和化妆品开发中，定量评估角质层的厚度和含水量被视为一种有用的度量方法。角质层负责大部分皮肤屏障功能，因此角质层的厚度和含水量成为关键因素。在本文中，我们将角质层视为电阻和电容的并联模型。通过测量皮肤的电阻抗，我们提出了一种新的模型，可以同时估算传统上使用共焦激光扫描显微镜和共焦拉曼光谱仪测量的角质层厚度和含水量，然后我们讨论了测量结果。我们使用了我们自行开发的设备来测量皮肤的电阻抗。测量开始后的3秒内，设备上的电极与皮肤接触，然后测量了使用两个不同频率的交流信号获得的电阻抗等参数。我们分别使用共焦激光显微镜和共焦拉曼光谱法测量了角质层的厚度和含水量；研究了角质层的厚度和含水量与皮肤电阻抗的关系；并建立了一个新的潜在模型，用于估算并联电阻和电容中的角质层的厚度和含水量。验证数据的相关系数分别为0.931和0.776；角质层厚度的均方根误差为2.3微米，而角质层表面的含水量的均方根误差为5.4个单位。这些发现表明，通过测量皮肤电阻抗，可以有效地定量评估角质层的厚度和含水量。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"内容记录\"><a href=\"#内容记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内容记录\"></a>内容记录</h3><p><strong>团队</strong>：Medical Engineering Laboratory, ALCARE CO., Ltd.;Department of Radiological Technology, Graduate School of Health Sciences, Okayama University</p>\n<p><strong>问题</strong>：通过测量皮肤电阻抗，可以有效地定量评估角质层的厚度和含水量</p>\n<p><strong>方法</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>使用了自行开发的设备来测量皮肤的电阻抗，使用<strong>两个不同频率</strong>的交流信号获得电阻抗等参数。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>分别使用<strong>共焦激光显微镜</strong>和<strong>共焦拉曼光谱法</strong>测量了角质层的<strong>厚度</strong>和<strong>含水量</strong>；</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>研究了<strong>角质层的厚度</strong>和<strong>含水量</strong>与<strong>皮肤电阻抗</strong>的关系；</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>建立新模型，由<strong>并联电阻和电容</strong>来估计角质层<strong>的厚度</strong>和<strong>含水量</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>效果</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>验证数据的相关系数分别为0.931和0.776；</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>角质层厚度的均方根误差为2.3微米，而角质层表面的含水量的均方根误差为5.4个单位。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>这些发现表明，通过测量皮肤电阻抗，可以有效地定量评估角质层的厚度和含水量。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>不足</strong>：样本人数应该增加，当皮肤表面涂有药物或出现特应性皮炎等疾病时，模型的理论条件可能不满足，需要找到提供更高灵敏度的信号频率</p>\n<h3 id=\"值得学习的地方\"><a href=\"#值得学习的地方\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"值得学习的地方\"></a>值得学习的地方</h3><p>transepidermal water loss (TEWL)</p>\n<p>electrical impendance method (IM)</p>\n<p>Confocal laser microscope 共焦激光显微镜</p>\n<p>Confocal Raman spectrometer 共焦拉曼光谱仪</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/image.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imageb.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imagec.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imaged.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imagee.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imagef.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imageg.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/SkinElectricalImpedanceModelforEvaluationoftheThicknessandWaterContentoftheStratumCorneum/imageh.png\"></p>\n<p>Multiple regression analysis</p>\n<p>the KH method</p>\n<p>得出实验数据之后，本文经过详细的discussion板块，探讨了结果的正确性，以及误差出现的原因，将来发展的方向，在此之后才给出了一个结论。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"论文基本信息第一作者：Osamu UEHARA, Toshimasa KUSUHARA,Kenichi MATSUZAKI, Yoshitake YAMAMOTO, Takao NAKAMURA 引用格式：[1]Osamu U,Toshimasa K,Kenichi M, et ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"ReadPaper","slug":"ReadPaper","count":10,"path":"api/categories/ReadPaper.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"皮肤电阻抗","slug":"皮肤电阻抗","count":1,"path":"api/tags/皮肤电阻抗.json"},{"name":"厚度","slug":"厚度","count":1,"path":"api/tags/厚度.json"},{"name":"含水量","slug":"含水量","count":1,"path":"api/tags/含水量.json"},{"name":"角质层","slug":"角质层","count":1,"path":"api/tags/角质层.json"},{"name":"皮肤屏障","slug":"皮肤屏障","count":1,"path":"api/tags/皮肤屏障.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">论文基本信息</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">摘要</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">内容记录</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%80%BC%